Titolo: Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles: The Crystal Bearers

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Final Fantasy Crystal Chronicles: The Crystal Bearers is a Wii action-adventure game announced at the Electronic Entertainment Expo. It was released on November 12, 2009 in Japan and on December 26 in North America. The game was well received in Japan, with praise for the game's well-written story and characters, but criticizing the map system. Western reviewers however were more mixed, citing that the game was less of a traditional RPG and more for action adventure.